      <h2>Let's Talk <span class="gold">Business</span></h2>
      <p>We welcome inquiries from traders, retailers, food processors, and international importers. Our team responds within 24 hours.</p>
      <div class="contact-details">
        <div class="cd-item">
          <div class="cd-icon">📧</div>
          <div>
            <strong>Email</strong>
            <span>info@alahmedriceagroexports.com</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="cd-item">
          <div class="cd-icon">📞</div>
          <div>
